				</ukm:Metadata><Primary><Body DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2026/11/body" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2026/11/body" NumberOfProvisions="374" RestrictExtent="E+W+S+N.I." RestrictStartDate="2026-05-18"><Part DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2026/11/part/1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2026/11/part/1" NumberOfProvisions="108" id="part-1" RestrictExtent="E+W+S+N.I." RestrictStartDate="2026-03-18"><Number>Part 1</Number><Title>Income tax, capital gains tax and corporate taxes</Title><Pblock DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2026/11/part/1/crossheading/income-tax-charge-rates-and-allowances" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2026/11/part/1/crossheading/income-tax-charge-rates-and-allowances" NumberOfProvisions="14" RestrictStartDate="2026-03-18" id="part-1-crossheading-income-tax-charge-rates-and-allowances" RestrictExtent="E+W+S+N.I."><Title>Income tax charge, rates and allowances</Title><P1group RestrictStartDate="2026-03-18" RestrictExtent="E+W+S+N.I."><Title>Freezing starting rate limit for savings for tax years 2026-27 to 2030-31</Title><P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2026/11/section/9" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2026/11/section/9" id="section-9"><Pnumber>9</Pnumber><P1para><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2026/11/section/9/1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2026/11/section/9/1" id="section-9-1"><Pnumber>1</Pnumber><P2para><Text>For the tax years 2026-27, 2027-28, 2028-29, 2029-30 and 2030-31, the amount specified in <Citation URI="https://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/section/12" id="c00009" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct" Year="2007" Number="3" SectionRef="section-12">section 12</Citation><Citation URI="https://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/section/12" id="c00010" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct" Year="2007" Number="3" SectionRef="section-12">(3)</Citation> of <Citation URI="https://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/contents" id="c00011" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct" Year="2007" Number="3" SectionRef="contents">ITA 2007</Citation> (the starting rate limit for savings) is “£5,000”.</Text></P2para></P2><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2026/11/section/9/2" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2026/11/section/9/2" id="section-9-2"><Pnumber>2</Pnumber><P2para><Text>Accordingly, <Citation URI="https://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/section/21" id="c00012" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct" Year="2007" Number="3" SectionRef="section-21">section 21</Citation> of <Citation URI="https://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/contents" id="c00013" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct" Year="2007" Number="3" SectionRef="contents">that Act</Citation> (indexation) does not apply in relation to the starting rate limit for savings for any of those tax years.</Text></P2para></P2></P1para></P1></P1group></Pblock></Part></Body></Primary></Legislation>